headline: Looking for Earnings Beat? Buy These 5 Top-Ranked Stocks
summary: Top-ranked stocks Urban Outfitters (URBN), Fox (FOX), Electronic Arts (EA), Uber Technologies (UBER) and Exelixis (EXEL) are likely to beat on the bottom line in their upcoming releases.
